What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Demand Response Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Demand Response Market

Demand response market will reach at an estimated value of USD 13.45 billion by 2028 and grow at a CAGR of 6.95% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Rise in the population is an essential factor driving the demand response market.

Demand response is defined as a type of change in the power consumption of an electric utility customer to better match the demand for power with the supply. Demand response seeks to adjust the continuous demand for power instead of adjusting the supply.

Rise in the volatile energy prices is a crucial factor accelerating the market growth, also increase in the disposable income, increase in the research and development activities in the market and rise in the demand from emerging economies are the major factors among others boosting the demand response market. Moreover, increasing technological advancements and modernization in the production techniques will further create new opportunities for demand response market in the forecast period mentioned above.

However, rise in the cost of research and development activities in the market is the major factor among others restraining the market growth, and will further challenge the demand response market in the forecast period mentioned above.

